ABUJA – The National Leader of the Ruling All Progressives Congress (APC), Asiwaju Bola Ahmed Tinubu has taken a swipe at critics who raise issues about his health and age that he’s coming to do brain work and President and not a concrete work requiring raw energy and agility. He APC chieftain is currently meeting with the APC Caucus of the House of Representatives in Abuja as part of his ongoing consultation ahead of the 2023 presidential race. Details shortly.